    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2243880/extras/3cde73d0abcfb5010af3b3756cc32b53.poster.avif?t=1676515242\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2243880/extras/3cde73d0abcfb5010af3b3756cc32b53.webm?t=1676515242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2243880/extras/3cde73d0abcfb5010af3b3756cc32b53.mp4?t=1676515242\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The Specter Chronicles is a cyberpunk visual novel that combines text-based adventure with turn-based tactical combat.<br><br>You are a Specter, a highly-trained enforcer of the Warden who rules over humanity as a godlike algorithmic entity. You have suffered a severe memory loss during a mission to track down the Prophet, a rebel leader who defies the Warden’s regime. With the help of a neural engineer, you must restore your memories by reliving them.<br><br>But what will you discover in your own memories?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore a dystopian world through branching narratives driven by your decisions</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2243880/extras/4bfdd65a29dc97884adb2e6e6d63fccb.poster.avif?t=1676515242\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2243880/extras/4bfdd65a29dc97884adb2e6e6d63fccb.webm?t=1676515242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2243880/extras/4bfdd65a29dc97884adb2e6e6d63fccb.mp4?t=1676515242\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Are you a brute who decimates everyone and everything that stands in your path? Or are you a smooth operator who prefers to avoid confrontation? The decision is yours.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Defeat your opponents using a unique combat system</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2243880/extras/b3993bc143523f77fd5e614ff3227fd7.poster.avif?t=1676515242\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2243880/extras/b3993bc143523f77fd5e614ff3227fd7.webm?t=1676515242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2243880/extras/b3993bc143523f77fd5e614ff3227fd7.mp4?t=1676515242\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Engage in turn-based combat where you can combine 6 basic attacks into combos, counters, and feints.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Tailor your gear to suit your fighting style</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2243880/extras/07f09a3c2b005f0a93d9973e0b062238.poster.avif?t=1676515242\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2243880/extras/07f09a3c2b005f0a93d9973e0b062238.webm?t=1676515242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2243880/extras/07f09a3c2b005f0a93d9973e0b062238.mp4?t=1676515242\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Install mods into your weapon and armor to infuse unique properties and functions, such as adding bonus points to an attribute or granting a buff during combat.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Randomized runs</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2243880/extras/352cce9a98817e5293cdde79edf4f77c.poster.avif?t=1676515242\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2243880/extras/352cce9a98817e5293cdde79edf4f77c.webm?t=1676515242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2243880/extras/352cce9a98817e5293cdde79edf4f77c.mp4?t=1676515242\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The fragments of memories that you encounter during a run will be randomly drawn, allowing you to revisit the memories that you want and discard the ones that you don’t.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >This game is for you if you…</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Enjoy text-based adventures that read like novellas.<br></li><li>Are looking for a break from card battlers and typical RPG combat - the combat system in The Specter Chronicles is definitely one-of-a-kind!<br></li><li>Are a comic book fan.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >This game is NOT for you if you…</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Don’t like text-heavy games.<br></li><li>Prefer action-based combat over turn-based combat.</li></ul>",
